title: Super Crossfire v1.1
description:
Old-school action meets dazzling graphic and energetic beats in Super Crossfire. Blast alien invaders while warping across the screen with an effortless tap. 

Unlock upgrades and acquire advanced power-ups as you seek to obliterate wave after wave of enemies. 

Boasting great replay value, intense action, and eye-popping visuals, Super Crossfire sets a new standard for arcade action.

Features:

* High intensity action + stylish graphics and music = pure fun
* 150 waves of alien-exterminating mayhem across 5 chapters
* Bonus unlockable Dark mode adds an additional 150 nail-biting waves
* Tilt, touch, or virtual button options--the choice is yours
